                                            <strong>Connexion bancaire sécurisée</strong>
                                        </h4>
                                        <p class="card-text text-muted">Synchronisation automatique de vos comptes bancaires. Plus besoin de saisir vos transactions manuellement.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                                <div class="card h-100 border-0" style="border-radius: 20px; transform: translateY(0); transition: transform 0.3s;">
                                    <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
                                        <div class="mb-4" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #00f2fe 100%); width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto;">
                                            <i class="fa fa-user fa-2x text-white"/>
                                        </div>
                                        <h4 class="card-title mb-3">
                                            <strong>Expert-comptable dédié</strong>
